column5: Toured all over the place and used some Balo spoons for a bit of pike and bass fishing!!  The ducks were relentless today.. lol. they went every where we did... i got some cool vids to upload when i get home.
Pet ducks are awesome!  Looks like a great time TJ.
Nice piccies TJ,  cant believe how tame those ducks are.
Nice spot, and I see you have all but one of your ducks in a row!!!
looks like an AC unit in pic 9 so I don't know if it's a "camp" or a "home" now TJ...
They must really miss you when you're not there  Great pics Teej!

Looks like a really relaxing time up there, Bud. Great pics, looking forward to the movies and talkies!  ps. Don't let the ducks get close to camp, they'll see the tripod, spinning twine and the turkey wire.
Must be feeding them "quackers"  Great post/photos, TJ!
Looks like you are living the dream bud!!! The camp is getting nicer and nicer.
I'm relaxed just looking ath the pics TJ. What a place to be right now. Thanks for sharing.   Paul
